<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <%- include('partials/head', { seo }) %>
</head>
<body>
    <%- include('partials/header') %>

    <main>

        <!-- ===== HERO ===== -->
        <section class="bm-hero">
            <div class="bm-hero-inner">
                <h1 class="bm-hero-title">From Order to Kitchen—Fully<br>Automated &amp; Error-Free</h1>
                <p class="bm-hero-subtitle">Bhojan Mitra removes manual handoffs between the counter and kitchen by automating every order, ensuring accuracy, speed, and zero confusion.</p>
                <a href="/contact" class="bm-btn-primary">Get started</a>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- ===== FEATURES ===== -->
        <section class="bm-features" id="features">
            <div class="bm-features-inner">

                <div class="bm-badge">Voice Ordering</div>

                <div class="rpos-feature-list">

                    <div class="rpos-feature">
                        <h3 class="rpos-feature-title">Direct Order-to-Kitchen Sync</h3>
                        <p class="rpos-feature-desc">When orders are placed through the Bhojan Mitra POS, they're instantly sent to kitchen displays and IoT devices. This eliminates handwritten notes and reduces errors. The result is faster service and happier customers. Our system ensures that every order is accurate and on time.</p>
                    </div>

                    <div class="rpos-feature">
                        <h3 class="rpos-feature-title">AI-Driven Order Accuracy</h3>
                        <p class="rpos-feature-desc">Our smart system automatically flags any discrepancies, such as missing ingredients or incorrect spice levels, before the order is finalized. This real-time validation ensures that every dish is prepared exactly as requested, maintaining quality and customer satisfaction. By catching errors early, we minimize waste and maximize efficiency in the kitchen. This leads to significant cost savings and a smoother operation.</p>
                    </div>

                    <div class="rpos-feature">
                        <h3 class="rpos-feature-title">Smarter Kitchen Flow, Less Food Waste</h3>
                        <p class="rpos-feature-desc">Real-time tracking ensures that every order is prepared in the correct sequence, minimizing bottlenecks and maximizing throughput. This level of control allows chefs to manage their stations effectively, reducing wait times and improving the overall dining experience. By optimizing kitchen workflows, restaurants can serve more customers without compromising on quality. The result is a smoother, more efficient operation that benefits both staff and patrons.</p>
                    </div>

                    <div class="rpos-feature">
                        <h3 class="rpos-feature-title">Peak-Hour Ready Operations</h3>
                        <p class="rpos-feature-desc">During peak times, Bhojan Mitra's system intelligently distributes orders, preventing bottlenecks and ensuring timely preparation. The kitchen display systems update in real-time, providing chefs with an accurate view of their tasks. This keeps everyone on the same page, from the front of house to the back, resulting in faster service and happier customers. Bhojan Mitra ensures your kitchen operates smoothly, no matter how busy it gets.</p>
                    </div>

                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- ===== CTA ===== -->
        <section class="rpos-cta">
            <div class="rpos-cta-inner">
                <h2 class="rpos-cta-title">Want to Know more</h2>
                <p class="rpos-cta-sub">Join the pilot to experience voice ordering, IoT routing, and analytics tailored to your restaurant before our public launch.</p>
                <a href="/contact" class="bm-btn-primary">Join the program</a>
            </div>
        </section>

    </main>

    <%- include('partials/footer') %>
    <script src="/js/main.js?v=<%= locals.assetVersion %>"></script>
</body>
</html>
